EN: Our friendship has gone through many tests.

ZH: 他们之间的情谊是无法撼动的。
EN: The bond between them is unshakable.

ZH: 感谢你对我的情谊，我会一直珍惜。
EN: Thank you for your friendship, I will cherish it always.

ZH: 这封信是我对你情谊的表达。
EN: This letter is my expression of friendship to you.

ZH: 他们之间的情谊维持了很多年。
EN: Their friendship has lasted for many years.

ZH: 友谊是一种深厚的情谊。
EN: Friendship is a deep bond.

ZH: 我们之间的情谊在困难时刻得到了体现。
EN: Our friendship was manifested in difficult times.

ZH: 情谊是建立在互相理解和信任的基础上的。
EN: Friendship is built on mutual understanding and trust.

ZH: 当他们需要帮助时，我会毫不犹豫地提供我的情谊。
EN: When they need help, I will readily offer my friendship.

